{"tid":578490,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"後生時，仲會覺得自己發到圍。","createTime":"2018-03-02T16:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T02:45:15.000Z","uid":63158,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da6fc72772d01e3a60ae650199c59e75754770a4","tid":578490,"uid":63158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"人越嚟越大時，就意識到根本冇可能。<br />\n<br />\n依家睇荷李活一線電影，見到裏面嘅童星/青少年雖然後生過我幾年，已經大有成就，前途無可限量；<br />\n<br />\n隔離post個12歲早熟女model, 人際仔細細ig已經有十幾萬followers;<br />\n<br />\n有個紀錄片頻道專訪兒童天才（youtube search child prodigy ）：有十幾歲嘅畫畫天才，一幅畫畫賣超過百萬港幣、又有鋼琴高手，十歲已經登台同著名樂手演奏jazz, 搞tour出碟又剩。<br />\n<br />\n望住自己，對比佢哋，知道造詣唔夠佢哋高，自然有啲心淡。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，「人比人，比死人」。但係人哋年紀輕輕就有咁高成就，真係睇到我有啲自卑。<br />\n<br />\n我既然無超卓造詣，就只好做個安分守己嘅平凡人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75890407324349b52fe5836e453afb532b0248b","tid":578490,"uid":75868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"呢個世界冇咁多平凡人又點襯托到佢係神童呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b802bf0a223a1abe48b96f4e19c4cb50eec1f5","tid":578490,"uid":111768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"屌 睇果啲特別例子緊係消沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下我地呢班偉大既連登仔 你就會發覺原來自己唔係咁廢同埋唔係單單淨係自己咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1642259d04404ac9693a6862adb029750388d6","tid":578490,"uid":45044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"最好笑係樓主以為只係得呢班人勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a247fd45b533d441a8abdae63dc1c1e4c1cc58d4","tid":578490,"uid":79023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"個個都發圍咁邊個炸脆香雞翼俾我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06096e8520945bf018ea575065592335e753c91","tid":578490,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:45:15.000Z","msg":"靠daddy好過"}]}